	<h1 class="title">QQ 音乐靠版权赚钱，第一个大单是网易云音乐</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/102277/small/102277.jpg?1432868256" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">韩方航 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-10-13 19:00:00 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/16028/medium/16028.jpg?1444720352" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


